  "remarks": "QDi.087\nSenior leader of Jemaah Islamiyah (QE.J.92.02). Brother of Gun Gun Rusman Gunawan (QI.G.218.06). In custody of the United States of America, as of Jul. 2007. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 1822 (2008) was concluded on 13 Apr. 2010. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2610 (2021) was concluded on 8 November 2022.; Listing: Listed by the UN 1267 Committee on 28 January 2003 (amended on 2 July 2007 and 27 Jul 2007, 16 May 2011, 6 Dec 2019, 8 Nov 2022)",
